data.content:
Canadian Dollar Scotiabank Visa Commercial Card	Coverage
insurance activation, payment requirement
The Canadian Dollar Scotiabank Visa Commercial Card must be used to pay for the rental to activate coverage.

Coverage	Rental Agency
rental conditions, insurance terms
Coverage is provided for rental vehicles from Rental Agencies, subject to specific terms and conditions.

Coverage	Eligible Persons
qualification criteria, insurance eligibility
Eligible Persons are those who qualify for coverage under specific conditions, including maintaining a Scotiabank Commercial Account.

Coverage	Third Party Liability
insurance exclusion, liability coverage
Third Party Liability is not covered under the insurance policy, requiring separate private insurance.

Coverage	Replacement Vehicle
insurance exclusion, personal coverage
Coverage does not apply to replacement vehicles if personal insurance covers the rental cost.

Coverage	Rental Period
duration limit, insurance terms
Coverage is limited to rental periods not exceeding 48 consecutive days.

Coverage	Narcotic Influence
coverage void, drug influence
Operating a vehicle under narcotic influence voids the insurance coverage.

Coverage	Seizure or Destruction
insurance exclusion, government action
Seizure or destruction by government or public authority is not covered by the insurance policy.

Coverage	War and Hostile Actions
insurance exclusion, war damage
Damages from war and hostile actions are excluded from the insurance policy.

Coverage	Nuclear Reaction
insurance exclusion, nuclear damage
Damages from nuclear reactions are not covered by the insurance policy.
